Package org.blockchainnative

Interface ContractWrapperGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EthereumContractWrapperGenerator, FabricContractWrapperGenerator
    public interface ContractWrapperGenerator
    Used to generate wrapper classes for calling smart contracts represented by ContractInfo objects.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    SmartContract, ContractInfo

    • Method Detail

      • generate

        <TContractInfo extends ContractInfo<TContractType,?,?>,TContractType> TContractType generate​(TContractInfo contractInfo)
        Generates a wrapper class for calling the smart contract represented by the given contract info.
        Type Parameters:
        TContractInfo - concrete type of contract info expected by the ContractWrapperGenerator
        TContractType - Java interface declaring the smart contracts methods and events
        Parameters:
        contractInfo - contract info representing the smart contract
        Returns:
        implementation of the given smart contract interface TContractType
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - in case the given contract info is null or not supported by the ContractWrapperGenerator, TContractType not an interface type
        ContractWrapperCreationException - in case an error occurs while creating the wrapper class

      • getWrapperName

        Returns the full name a of the smart contract wrapper class represented by a the given contract info.
        Parameters:
        contractInfo - contract info representing the smart contract
        Returns:
        package name + class name of the generated wrapper class
